{"tid":47262,"cid":28,"subCid":0,"title":"［肥婆icon] 解決方法其實好容易","createTime":"2016-12-20T08:23:39.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-20T08:42:14.000Z","uid":10009,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"08acae76f84f391bb0f2fd7bc7b81698519a76b3","tid":47262,"uid":10009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T08:23:39.000Z","msg":"其實點做都有人反對 <br />\n既然每個大都有自己睇法同自由 咁不如由會員自己決定睇唔睇到某種特定icon啦<br />\n<br />\n其實肥婆icon 會對應返連登最基本既icon，例如<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> = #<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />#fatc <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  = #<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />#fatc <br />\n<br />\n只要係個app度比人揀到底係enable 定 disable 隻icon<br />\n咁就可以比符合晒每個user既preference <br />\n<br />\n如果係disable既，咪出返原icon <br />\n例如 #<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />#fatc 就出返 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />fatc 就出返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6edcd223620fcd531b54f78cba1460f033723f14","tid":47262,"uid":50533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T08:24:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9116c68905eefc26a2d227b2b9264057b0c801ae","tid":47262,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T08:24:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />fatc 咁呢啲呢"},{"pid":"73f42f1d5cb23d6bc6301e80b7e0ab9edc73645f","tid":47262,"uid":10009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T08:26:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />fatc 咁呢啲呢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無對應既就直情熄咗佢<br />\n管理員都應該要有指引，如果要採用會員設計既icon, 應該要限制住就icon要有原生icon既對應，etc"},{"pid":"42ef085b252dd62322bcd1612beb4492126bd71f","tid":47262,